Detailed Description

cvmx_uahc::_gsbuscfg1

This register can be used to configure the core after power-on or a change in mode of operation. This register mainly contains AXI system-related configuration parameters. Do not change this register after the initial programming. The application must program this register before starting any transactions on AXI.

This register can be reset by IOI reset or with UCTL()_CTL[UAHC_RST].
